          "_name": "features036",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features036\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<header>Card</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Title\" name=\"showCardTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Card Subtitle\" name=\"showCardSubtitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f80808\" selected>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t<header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 content-head mb-5\">\n\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style  mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<b>Outros serviços</b></h1>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\"><b>\n\t\t\t\t\tSolicite informações : ceo.ojohn@gmail.com</b></p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 item-mb active\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-left item-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3 mbr-number\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Treinamentos</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Capacitação que Inspira: Feita para Você!</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\">Entendemos que pessoas como você são a nossa maior inspiração. Por isso, oferecemos treinamentos personalizados, desenvolvidos na medida exata para atender às suas necessidades e potencializar o seu desenvolvimento.\n<br>\n<br>Seja para aprimorar suas habilidades, aprender algo novo ou avançar em sua carreira, nossos programas são feitos para impulsionar o seu crescimento.\n<br>\n<br>Pronto para transformar sua jornada?\n<br>\n<br>Começando por:\n<br>Pocket Course Conceitos Básicos: IA  \n<br>e outros +\n<br>\n<br>[Presencial - Hibrido - Remoto]\n<br>- na sua empresa\n<br>- na sua comunidade (condomínios, clubes, associações)\n<br>\n<br>\n<br><br></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"index.html#features036-1o\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">+ info</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 item-mb\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\" align-left item-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3 mbr-number\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Mentoria e Consultoria</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Mentor de tecnologia estratégica sob demanda!</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\"><br>Conte sobre sua necessidade e encontraremos uma solução juntos para o seu negócio.\n<br>\n<br><b>Fale conosco: ceo.ojohn@gmail.com</b><br></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"page1.html#pricing03-1l\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">+ info</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4 item-mb\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"align-left item-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3 mbr-number\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-number\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Super apps as a service</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Aplicativos para o seu negócio</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\">Desenvolvimento ágil em plataformas de lnteligência artificial NoCode, para solução de necessidades específicas e especiais do seu negócio.<br><br>Rápido, prático e com custo baixo.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"page1.html#pricing03-1l\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">+ info</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
